| 分配线索 | HTTP请求 | `POST /api/training-leads/miniprogram/{id}/assign` | 指定跟进人（默认同时设为 studentOwner） | `{assignedTo, studentOwner?}` | `{success, data: TrainingLead}` | `training-lead:edit` |
| 更新线索状态 | HTTP请求 | `POST /api/training-leads/miniprogram/{id}/update-status` | 直接修改 `status`（如改"无效线索"） | `{status}` | `{success, data: TrainingLead}` | `training-lead:edit` |
| 删除线索 | HTTP请求 | `POST /api/training-leads/miniprogram/{id}/delete` | 软删除前留操作日志 | `{id}`（path） | `{success}` | `training-lead:delete` |
| 获取统计数据 | HTTP请求 | `GET /api/training-leads/miniprogram/statistics` | 看板统计：总数/各状态/来源/跟进数 | 无 | 见"统计返回结构" | `training-lead:view` |
| 获取表单枚举 | HTTP请求 | `GET /api/training-leads/miniprogram/options` | 所有下拉枚举（性别 / 来源 / 职位 / 等级 / 状态 / 跟进方式与结果 / 意向课程） | 无 | `{success, data: { genderOptions, leadSourceOptions, consultPositionOptions, intentionLevelOptions, leadGradeOptions, statusOptions, followUpTypeOptions, followUpResultOptions, intendedCoursesOptions }}` | `training-lead:view` |

